text: Capel George Pett Pownall was an archer from Great Britain. He was born on 28 November 1868 and died on 8 February 1933. Pownall competed at the 1908 Summer Olympics.Capel PownallCapel POWNALL == References == Category:1869 births Category:1933 deaths Category:British archers Category:Olympians for Great Britain
